realm

　核心词汇　
英 [relm] 　　美 [relm] 　　

  • n. 领域；王国
  • 

new

realm的英文翻译是什么意思，词典释义与在线翻译：

详尽释义

n. (名词)

 1. 领域
 2. 范围
 3. 王国
 4. 界
 5. 国土
 6. 区域
 7. 部门
 8. 圈
 9. 带
10. 天下
11. 地方
12. 空间
13. 场所
14. 领土
15. 国度
16. 地域

双解释义

n. (名词)

 1. [C]领域,范围 range; scope
 2. [C]王国,国度 a kingdom

英英释义

Noun:

 1. a domain in which something is dominant;

    "the untroubled kingdom of reason"
    "a land of make-believe"
    "the rise of the realm of cotton in the south"

 2. the domain ruled by a king or queen

 3. a knowledge domain that you are interested in or are communicating about;

    "it was a limited realm of discourse"
    "here we enter the region of opinion"
    "the realm of the occult"

realm的用法和样例：

例句

用作名词 (n.)

 1. They exist only in the physical realm.
    它们只存在于物质感官的领域。
 2. He made outstanding contributions in the realm of foreign affairs.
    他在外交领域作出了卓越贡献。
 3. The material realm is one area that everyone relates to.
    物质领域是与每个人有联系的一个地方。
 4. He was banished from the realm.
    他被驱逐出境。
 5. The king banished the traitor from the realm.
    国王把背叛者驱逐出王国。
 6. A philosopher dwells in the realm of ideas.
    哲学家停留在概念的王国里。

常见句型

用作名词 (n.)

 1. Their failures in the realm have damaged their self-confidence and
    creditability.
    他们在本领域的失败使他们的自信心和可信度受损。
 2. The creature has the largest eyes in the whole animal realm.
    在整个动物界中这种动物眼睛最大。
 3. The king was concerned about the safety of the realm.
    国王十分关心王国的安全。

词汇搭配

用作名词 (n.)
形容词+～

  • political realm 政治领域

介词+～

  • in the realm of 在…方面,在…领域
  • within the realm of possibility 在可能的范围内

～+介词

  • realm of necessity 必然王国
  • realm of science 科学领域
  • realm of the superstructure 上层建筑领域

经典引文

  • That the Realm of England should be destroyed through the misgovernance of
    King Richard.

    出自： R. Baker
  • A..coin of the realm.

    出自： Day Lewis
  • My motives are lofty, but my work now takes place in the realm of the
    everyday.

    出自： P. Auster
  • Freud ventures outside the clinical realm to make observations on humanity
    as a whole.

    出自： M. Bergmann

realm的详细讲解：

词源解说

  • ☆ 13世纪晚期进入英语，直接源自古法语的reaume，意为王国；最初源自拉丁语的
    regimen，意为政府体制。

